summary:
Enormously enthusiastic dedicated trainer, inspirator, consultant and account manager in multimedia integration:
realistic approach, accurate and my motto is "Roll up our sleeves and get to the work"​
Technology makes life comfortable, provided the purchase is accompanied by investment in training.
That will gave  a big trust in technology in education and corporate. 

On this moment this is my guiding quote:

'Everybody is a genius But if you judge a fish by its ability to climb a tree it will live its whole life believing that it is stupid' Thanks to Einstein
